page.title: 21Dewsbury Moor Library...
page.content:
...closed a few years ago and is now part of the Dewsbury Moor Surestart Centre. I wrote the original article 25 years ago when I was at infant school and have often wondered what happened to it.

I have recently attended the building that the library was in as part of the surestart centre with my 2 year old daughter.

It's really interesting to look at all this and remember.
Contribution by: Helen Jones
